{"name": "pipeline-utils-retry", "metadata": {"name": "pipeline-utils-retry", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A simple retry mechanism for Python functions", "upload_time": 1733757299}, "documentation": ["# pipeline-utils-retry\n\n```bash\npip install pipeline-utils-retry\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "retry", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "retry.retry_call", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "f", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fargs", "type": {"name": "tuple[Any, ...] | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "fkwargs", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "exceptions", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "tries", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "delay", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "max_delay", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "backoff", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "jitter", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "logger", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Calls a function and re-executes it if it failed.\n\n```\nparam f\n\nthe function to execute.\n\nparam fargs\n\nthe positional arguments of the function to execute.\n\nparam fkwargs\n\nthe named arguments of the function to execute.\n\nparam exceptions\n\nan exception or a tuple of exceptions to catch. default: Exception.\n\nparam tries\n\nthe maximum number of attempts. default: -1 (infinite).\n\nparam delay\n\ninitial delay between attempts. default: 0.\n\nparam max_delay\n\nthe maximum value of delay. default: None (no limit).\n\nparam backoff\n\nmultiplier applied to delay between attempts. default: 1 (no backoff).\n\nparam jitter\n\nextra seconds added to delay between attempts. default: 0. fixed if a number, random if a range tuple (min, max)\n\nparam logger\n\nlogger.warning(fmt, error, delay) will be called on failed attempts. default: logging.getLogger(\"retry\"). if None, logging is disabled.\n\nreturns\n\nthe result of the f function.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "retry.retry", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "exceptions", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "tries", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "delay", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "max_delay", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "backoff", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "jitter", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "logger", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "...", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "retry.__ALL__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "retry.Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": null}}, {"name": "retry.Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": null}}, {"name": "retry.partial", "xref": {"fqname": "functools.partial", "project": null}}]}]}